@node Requirements " Requirements "

 .oO @{b}REQUIREMENTS@{ub} Oo.


-  You  will  need at least Kickstart 2.0.  Small MagicWB is supporting all
   Kickstart/Workbench versions beginning from version 2.0.

-  MagicWB supports OS3.x in a special way: OS3.x users will benefit from a
   better palette, a better color handling and AGA-Patterns.

-  You should use a 'non-proportional' resolution like Hires.
   (pixels are about twice as high as they are wide)

@endnode
